title: In Gurgaon's High-Rise Collapse That Killed 2, Grave New Charges By Cops - NDTV
content: In Gurgaon's High-Rise Collapse That Killed 2, Grave New Charges By Cops  NDTV
description: Realty firm Chintels India had on Friday said the company is cooperating with the local authorities on the "unfortunate" incident and would conduct a structural audit of the entire project.
